query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS security_logs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId INT NULL,
  companyId INT NULL,
  action VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  metadata JSON NULL,
  ipAddress VARCHAR(45) NULL,
  userAgent TEXT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
